The paper discusses the combination of probability with logics for modeling the world, which is a common topic in artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and logic (cs.LO) research. The paper also presents a system for computing the probability of queries w.r.t. probabilistic knowledge bases, which is related to database (cs.DB) research. Additionally, the paper discusses reasoning and learning algorithms, which are topics in natural language processing (cs.CL) and cryptography (cs.CR).
